# File Naming Conventions

> **Topic unit architecture (this repo)**: See [09_week-companion-architecture.mdc](./09_week-companion-architecture.mdc) for on-demand creation rules and topic governance.

## Topic file numbering

- **Start at `01_`**: File numbering starts at `01_` (never `00_`).
- **Sequential**: Use `01_`, `02_`, `03_`, … as topics are added.
- **Kebab-case slug**: `01_spec-first-design.md`, `02_eval-loop-patterns.md`.

## File naming pattern (within topic folders)

| Folder | Example file names |
|--------|--------------------|
| `src/notes/` | `01_sdd-foundations.md`, `02_deterministic-ai.md` |
| `src/specs/` | `01_prompt-contract-template.md`, `02_behavior-spec-example.md` |
| `src/evals/` | `01_eval-loop-design.md`, `02_eval-metrics.md` |
| `src/patterns/` | `01_spec-first-pattern.md`, `02_prompt-versioning.md` |
| `src/experiments/` | `01_first-spec-experiment.md` |
| `docs/` | `01_repository-structure.md`, `agent-skills.md` |

## Images & figures

- Descriptive kebab-case (e.g. `spec-flow-diagram.png`).
- Stored alongside or in a subfolder of the relevant topic folder.
